name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 14, the owners of Donghaiwanmendi went to the municipal government again to protest against the conversion of the community sales office into a nuclear medicine medical testing center.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: A blogger from Xi'an disclosed the phone call from Yanjiao police asking him to delete his post. After he said he would not delete the post, the police said, "If you don't delete it, the public security organs will contact you later..."

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: A cordon has been set off around the explosion site in Yanjiao, Hebei

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: Next to the cordon, a woman sat on the roadside crying

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
Recently, a video of a woman kneeling in front of the statue of Bao Gong and crying loudly in Bao Gong Temple in Kaifeng, Henan Province, went viral and triggered a copycat effect. More and more people who have suffered injustice and have nowhere to seek redress have gone to Bao Gong Temple and cried.
On March 14, ID: "Judicial Corruption Fighter abc" posted a message saying that she was the woman in the video and the reason she knelt in front of the statue of Bao Gong and cried was because she won the lawsuit in Changtu Court, but the court cheated and let go of the seized property. A few days ago, I went to my cousin's house in Kaifeng and saw the statue of Bao Gong while playing. I couldn't control myself for a while, so I knelt in front of the statue of Bao Gong and cried loudly.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: At 6:35 on March 15, a traffic accident occurred on the west side of the intersection of Jinhan Highway and Jingsan Road in Dongli District, Tianjin, where a coach and a public bus rear-ended each other, resulting in one death and 37 injuries. According to a staff member of the Propaganda Department of the Dongli District Party Committee of Tianjin, the bus was carrying students in the first and second year of high school.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 12, a fire broke out in a warehouse of Dingguagua Gas Distribution Factory in Zhongluotan Town, Baiyun District, Guangzhou. When reporters from Guangdong TV and other media went to the scene for interviews, they were blocked by the Public Security Committee of Guangzhou Baiyun District Public Security Bureau.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: After the Yanjiao explosion, netizens from many places said that their communities had experienced forced buying and selling under the pretext of safety inspections.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 14, Yanjiao, Hebei. In Yanjiao Park, diagonally opposite the scene of the incident, residents placed seven bouquets of flowers to commemorate the seven victims of the incident.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 14, a blogger from Shandong said that he had posted a video of a recent car accident in Handan, Hebei, to remind people not to drink and drive. He then received a call, in which the other party advised the blogger to delete the video and said that the blogger's mobile phone number had been included in the big database monitoring, and posting videos randomly would not do him any good.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content: On March 15, the property owners' committee of Xinluo Yunshu Community in Longyan, Fujian, signed a contract with the new property management company without the consent of the owners. On the same day, the new property management company forcibly moved into the community and a fierce confrontation broke out with the owners and the old property management company.
